This is the simple led blink module that use timer to set the period of blinking
Tested on RPi Zero, use GPIO pin 23 to control led

Features:
	*Supports ability to pass period as module parameter `insmod hello.ko period=<some period in milliseconds>`
		When period is not pass, the module use default value of 1000ms
	*Pass current led state and period to /proc/hello/drv_info

